{"tid":793550,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[後備機] Nokia X5 試玩","createTime":"2018-08-25T13:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T02:12:53.000Z","uid":78399,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"255111f6d25db7cc211567d426a9d7615d95d20b","tid":793550,"uid":78399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"Nokia X5 簡單開箱<br />\n<br />\n淘寶官方站買既 人仔999 (3+32) dual 4G sim<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開個盒先知Nokia 送埋個case<br />\n早知唔另外買case<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/213643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F213643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=269ceebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面堆涵係咁， 得說明文同叉電器<br />\n叉電器當然係兩腳， 話哂部機係大陸版<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/213721_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F213721_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1aa629a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部機造工幾好， 唔覺係低階機<br />\n好似用左2.5D玻璃<br />\n另外呢隻色好靚， 叫波羅海藍<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/213756_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F213756_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3e1d4209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好熟悉既開機畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/213812_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F213812_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9ad26ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開完機，就即刻收到 updates<br />\n係八月security package , system stability之類<br />\n<br />\nFYI, goolge store google chrome要係原生app store download<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/213829_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F213829_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6cd8ce12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢有個floating circle類似HTC 既function,可叫放你想放既apps , or wifi 之類 比你quick access<br />\n另外， 有類似3D touch 功能<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/213845_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F213845_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=276b0afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/214212_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F214212_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9721970c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後介紹埋一個幾好用既function, 兩隻手指長按堆文字， 例如新聞。 佢會打散堆字比你search<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/213915_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F213915_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=28346190&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3df9a78cd0bc892100987fb6a9b508210454e3d8","tid":793550,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"正wo, 順豐送貨？"},{"pid":"909699db50ce67f7388a95ce95581a35757b2bad","tid":793550,"uid":78399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3df9a78cd0bc892100987fb6a9b508210454e3d8","tid":793550,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"正wo, 順豐送貨？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:05:25.000Z","msg":"我用集運， 順便買堆case<br />\n補張跑分相，3+32 大約13萬分<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/220458_ea